asset.author: Hoover
asset.hookText: We designed the T-Series vacuum to be easy to maintain, so it should continue to have great suction throughout the life of the vacuum. If you're experiencing loss of suction or having problems getting your Hoover WindTunnel T-Series to pick up dirt, we can help! This short video will take you through some easy troubleshooting tips that should get rid of any clogs or other problems that could be causing your vacuum's loss of suction.
